# help/

Help documentation for Intent CLI commands. Each `.help.md` file provides detailed usage information, options, and examples for a specific intent subcommand.

## Files

- `claude.help.md` -- Claude Code integration (subagents, skills, rules, upgrade, prime)
- `agents.help.md` -- AGENTS.md management (initialize, sync, validate agent instructions)
- `wp.help.md` -- Work package management (create, list, track within steel threads)
- `modules.help.md` -- Module registry (Highlander enforcement, detect unregistered modules)
- `audit.help.md` -- Code quality checks (Credo, custom rules, auto-fix, health reports)
- `rules.help.md` -- Rule library (enumerate, validate, index rules across languages)
- `learn.help.md` -- Capture learnings (footguns, patterns worked/failed for sessions)
- `plugin.help.md` -- Plugin discovery (list, show, help for Intent plugins)
- `ext.help.md` -- User extensions (list, validate, scaffold at ~/.intent/ext/)
- `fileindex.help.md` -- File indexing (create indexes with checkbox states)
- `stzero.help.md` -- Steel Thread Zero retrofit (onboard projects, audit deliverables)
